6:
Hmm. Awfully quiet today, isn't it?
Where are all the monsters?
10:
Yeah. This might be a good day to
try delving a little bit deeper than
usual.
17: It's really dangerous over there! See?
28:
Those are some sharp eyes you
have.
Who might you be?
34:
My name is Ritta!
I'm a professional scout!
36:
You do know what a scout is, don't
you?
42:
A scout is a person sent out to
survey the land and perform
reconnaissance.
Am I correct?
46:
Yes, yes! That was perfect.
It's my job to spot dangerous
situations from afar—and prevent
them, of course.
48:
We scouts are a must-have on any
adventure!
55:
Today I'm offering a special deal!
You can avail yourselves of my
scouting services for FREE!
58:
Normally I'd charge quite a hefty fee
for this, but... today's your lucky day!
70:
It can't hurt!
Show us the way, Ritta!
75:
Good news, good news!
I've spotted a deposit of
high-quality elemental ore over in
that direction!
80:
Wow, our luck is really something
today. First we get a guide for free,
now this!
83:
Hehehe.
Don't stop there, keep the
compliments coming!
86:
People often say that scouts are
uncool, or boring. They look down on
us... but the truth is we're very, very
useful!
91:
Oh my...
That is an enormous amount of
treasure!
95:
There is even a treasure chest as
well.
101:
Oooh, there's sure to be good stuff
inside! Open it, open it!
108:
Odd that there's just one chest
here... Hmm.
114: Ahh! Wh-what on earth is this?!
118:
HEHEHE! That's what we call a
jack-in-the-box! Surprise!
120:
Oh man, you should have seen your
reaction!
I love it when a prank goes off
perfectly!
122:
A prank?
I figured it was a trap or
something—you know I thought I
was about to die, right?!
126:
O-oh. Sorry! My bad, whoops.
Totally.
I apologize. Really.
130:
That's an unconvincing apology if
I've ever heard one.
Why did you go through all this
trouble? Are you that bored?
136: Is all this treasure also yours, Ritta?
141:
Hehe. I'm sorry, that reaction was
just so... fresh! That might be my
favorite one so far!
146:
Uh-oh. Danger spotted in the
distance.
But no worries!
148:
Ritta's got the solution ready to go!
A handcrafted, special item that
solves any problem! What is it, you
ask?
159:
And that concludes my tour for the
day. Great work, everyone!
163:
That was certainly an eventful day...
but a pretty good one overall, I think!
166:
Hey, you're that scout girl, aren't
you? Are you still working for the day?
168:
If you don't have any jobs lined up,
I've got one tomorrow you could do.
Could you help me? No pranks,
though, please and thank you.
172:
Actually, I have plans tomorrow!
Find someone else to do it!
177: Are you sure that was okay to do?
181:
Yep, yep!
Reason being, those guys are a
TOTAL bore to prank. Zero reaction.
184:
But you guys... Now those are some
faces that I want to see! All freaked
out, eyes wide open—that was great!
187:
Anyway, if you ever need any
scouting done, you know who to
call! I offer complimentary pranks as
well, of course!
191:
We could do without the pranks, to
be honest...
196:
Or maybe just cut down on the
pranks where I think I'm about to
die? Not a fan of those ones.
